- **Textbooks:**  
  - *Linear Algebra Done Right* – Sheldon Axler  
  - *Engineering Mathematics* – GATE Academy Publications  

- **Practice Problems:**  
  - [GATE Previous Year Questions](https://gateoverflow.in/questions/tagged/eigenvalues)  
